{
  "stem": "9168.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was only through a British-- a BBC correspondent, an American, that I learned that her father was the head of the Chicago Bund in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Huber.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our freelance reporting office, into our office came a flyer-- a printed flyer from the United States War Department, recruiting court reporters.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this must have been in 19-- the early part of 1945.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The war ended on May 8th, '45, and they were going to go to trial in Germany on the major Nazi leaders in November.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that date had not been set.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew they needed a lot of court reporters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So these flyers went out, I understood, into every major court reporting office in major cities of the United States, the large cities, recruiting approximately 26 court reporters to go to Germany to report Goering's trial, get started.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I understood later that other reporters in other cities did not know about it, because the principals in their offices did not want to lose them to Germany or Japan and for the Japanese war trials.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they did not let them have the knowledge of this flyer which was sent.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my boss did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He let us know about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I applied immediately.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, by that time, I had become intrigued with what was going on, maybe stemming from my friendship with that German in [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Graig ?] College.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was German, and all my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow I just had a feeling that I needed to go to Germany and work on these trials.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because, by that time, 1945, knowledge about these massacres was coming out in the press.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I applied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew I had the speed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had the skill.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
